<subSubSection pageId="10" pageNumber="11" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="10.[151,1436,151,374]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,353,151,177]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Description:</emphasis>
<emphasis box="[362,494,152,177]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Male Adult</emphasis>
: Unknown. 
<emphasis box="[644,804,152,177]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Female Adult</emphasis>
(pinned): Length. Body, 2.0 mm; forewing, 4.0 mm. Body dark brown to black. Legs brown becoming pale brown distally. Forewing (
<figureCitation box="[1125,1234,190,216]" captionStart="FIGURES 21–25" captionStartId="6.[151,271,1911,1935]" captionTargetBox="[227,1368,439,1875]" captionTargetId="figure-151@6.[212,1376,426,1887]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURES 21–25. Leptohyphes apache, larval structures. 21, head and prothorax, [scale bar B]. 22, foreleg [D]. 23, hindleg [E]. 24, hind claw (ventro-lateral) [C]. 25, abdominal tergites 7-10 [A]. Scale bars (mm): A, B = 0.05; C = 0.1; D = 0.5; E = 0.4." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5305027" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5305027/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Fig. 25E</figureCitation>
): reddish-brown; vein CuP not strongly curved towards A; vein ICu 
<subScript attach="left" box="[772,780,245,259]" fontSize="6" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">2</subScript>
free
<subScript attach="left" box="[836,840,245,259]" fontSize="6" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">;</subScript>
ICu 
<subScript attach="left" box="[892,900,245,259]" fontSize="6" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">1</subScript>
attached basally to CuA by crossvein; MP 
<subScript attach="right" box="[1428,1436,245,259]" fontSize="6" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">2</subScript>
united basally to IMP by cross veins. Legs: yellowish to pale reddish-brown to grey, with basal blackish shading. Hind wing absent. Abdomen. Dark brown with black markings. 
<emphasis box="[1010,1080,310,335]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Larva</emphasis>
: Unknown.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
